section
  h2 Feature detection vs browser sniffing
  p <b>USER AGENT SNIFFING</b>
  pre
    code.
      var dateSupport =
        browser != 'IE' &&
        !(browser === 'Mozilla' && version < 4) &&
        !(browser === 'Webkit' && version < 1.5)
      ;
  p <b>FEATURE DETECTION</b>
  pre
    code.
      var dateSupport =
        (new Element('input', { type: 'date' }).type === 'date');

